The '''Loronar Navy''' was the defense space fleet of [[Loronar/Legends|Loronar]]. They were known for their search for the [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] [[Reginald Barkbone]]. The swashbuckling freebooter subsequently recalled this pursuit as his "worst spell in space", although he claimed it was because he was stuck with a vegetarian galley droid.

